data.description: Looking for quiet and peace of country living? This 4 bdrm, 2 bath home is where you will find it.  Home is secluded back off the road, partial timber and surrounded by a big yard. Front porch spans across the front of the home. Great for your early morning coffee or relaxing after work. Large kitchen, dining, and living area. Perfect for family and friend get togethers. Huge master bedroom and master bath. Master bath includes make-up table and a garden tub. Large pantry off of the kitchen. Laundry room has sink and counter for folding clothes. Laundry also has an exterior door for easy access from the outside. Pantry, laundry and walk-in closets have smart lighting.  All cabinets are real wood made in Arkansas. All doors are 36" wide. The property abounds with deer, rabbits and other wildlife.  Property is close to Genoa Schools and 10 minutes from the Loop in Texarkana
